movie.title: The Haunted World of El Superbeasto
movie.title_english: The Haunted World of El Superbeasto
movie.title_long: The Haunted World of El Superbeasto (2009)
movie.description_intro: The story follows the adventures of El Superbeasto, a washed-up Mexican luchador, and his sultry sidekick and sister Suzi-X as they confront an evil villain by the name of Dr. Satan. The adventure, set in the mythic world of Monsterland, also has a character named Murray the robot.

movies.title: The First Power
movies.summary: A killer is given the gas chamber after committing several demonic murders. His spirit is released and given power by the Devil. Now the cop that caught him before must find a way to do it again.

movies.title: V/H/S Viral
movies.summary: V/H/S: Viral is a 2014 American anthology horror film from Bloody Disgusting. The final film in the V/H/S trilogy, created by Brad Miska, features a series of found-footage shorts written and directed by Nacho Vigalondo, Marcel Sarmiento, Gregg Bishop, Justin Benson and Aaron Scott Moorhead.

movies.title: Crazy Birds
movies.summary: It's springtime in Fernville, and that means it's time for the annual talent show, where the jungle animals get to show off their singing skills! Birds Marshall and Mimi are a show favorite, but local music guru, Marlon Pintop, is not pleased!

movies.title: AKA Jane Roe
movies.summary: Final series of interviews prior to Norma McCorvey's death and reveals the unvarnished truth behind her journey from pro-choice to pro-life and beyond - in what she calls her "deathbed confession.
